quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,52,"Ith dakhaloo AAalayhi faqaloosalaman qala inna minkum wajiloon"
  15,53,"Qaloo la tawjal innanubashshiruka bighulamin AAaleem"
  15,54,"Qala abashshartumoonee AAalaan massaniya alkibaru fabima tubashshiroon"
  15,55,"Qaloo bashsharnaka bilhaqqifala takun mina alqaniteen"
  15,56,"Qala waman yaqnatu min rahmatirabbihi illa addalloon"
  15,57,"Qala fama khatbukumayyuha almursaloon"
  15,58,"Qaloo inna orsilna ilaqawmin mujrimeen"
  15,59,"Illa ala lootin innalamunajjoohum ajmaAAeen"
  15,60,"Illa imraatahu qaddarna innahalamina alghabireen"
  15,61,"Falamma jaa ala lootinalmursaloon"
  15,62,"Qala innakum qawmun munkaroon"
  15,63,"Qaloo bal ji/naka bimakanoo feehi yamtaroon"
  15,64,"Waataynaka bilhaqqiwa-inna lasadiqoon"
  15,65,"Faasri bi-ahlika biqitAAin minaallayli wattabiAA adbarahum wala yaltafitminkum ahadun wamdoo haythutu/maroon"
  15,66,"Waqadayna ilayhi thalikaal-amra anna dabira haola-i maqtooAAunmusbiheen"
  15,67,"Wajaa ahlu almadeenati yastabshiroon"
  15,68,"Qala inna haola-i dayfeefala tafdahoon"
  15,69,"Wattaqoo Allaha walatukhzoon"
  15,70,"Qaloo awa lam nanhaka AAani alAAalameen"
